			Privacy Policy
		</h1>
		<p>Last updated: March 20, 2024</p>
		<h2>
			Information we collect
		</h2>
		<p>
			We collect
			<ul>
				<li>
					your Discord account details (username, and whether you are part of the "osu! Logo Builders" Discord server), 
				</li>
				<li>
					your osu! account details (username, preferred gamemode, global leaderboard position, country leaderboard position, the country who's leaderboard you participate in, total performance points, and total play count), 
				</li>
				<li>
					and the username(s) of your Discord account's connected Reddit account(s) (but only if you are part of the "osu! Logo Builders" Discord server).
				</li>
			</ul>
		</p>
		<h2>
			How we use and share your information
		</h2>
