			We may use your e-mail address for important notifications (for example, notifying you of a data breach), but we won't use it for any other purposes such as marketing.
		</p>-->
		<p>
			We may share your information as required by law (i.e. to comply with a request from law enforcement).
		</p>
		<p>
			We won't sell your information to any third-parties or use it for any purposes other than the ones described in this privacy policy.
		</p>
		<h2>
			Data retention
		</h2>
		<p>
			We'll store your data as long as necessary to provide our services, or until you disconnect the Application within either osu!'s or Discord's account settings.
		</p>
		<h2>
			Contact
		</h2>
		<p>
			If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@osu.place">contact@osu.place</a> or in our Discord server.
		</p>
